Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak jumpa. Aku Toda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini, aku yang akan\Nmembersihkan rumahmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, kau belum dengar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita sudah mengundurkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dia rajin dan bisa diandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku mulai bersih-bersih, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana penyedot debunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kinoshita...\N- Coba kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mengundurkan diri?\N- Ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage, lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemotretan Tamon edisi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senyumnya sungguh sempurna bak dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage tampak murung belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kelihatan linglung.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat lupakan Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembalilah ke masa saat jadi penggemar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatku bahagia seperti dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan yang terbaik\Nuntuk mendukung Tamon sebagai idola.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat tinggal, Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepada semua pacarku di seluruh dunia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lagu apa yang harus memelukmu malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih sudah ada di dunia ini.\N- Kepada semua pacarku di seluruh dunia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hari ini, aku memikirkan jarak...\N- lagu apa yang harus memelukmu malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- di antara alis Tamon\N- Kepada semua pacarku di seluruh dunia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- sambil makan.\N- lagu apa yang harus memelukmu malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepada semua…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Tuan Suram ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu memikirkan Suram, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Hottiehara tak cukup lagi untukmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti berbohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau yang menerkam Suram?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya suka Hottiehara.\NTolong maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tega sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita, kau jahat sekali…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu tadi mimpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat melihat Hottiehara,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku langsung teringat Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku menyingkirkan\Nbarang-barangnya untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pikiranku masih saja kacau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uta, kau tidak asyik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang biasa kulakukan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebelum jadi penggemar Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menyingkirkan Tamon dari hidupku,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu apa yang tersisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, gelap sekali di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu dan ayah akan pulang larut malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kau sudah menyingkirkan\Nbarang-barangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah membersihkan kamarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah sadar kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya menyimpannya sebentar\Nuntuk menenangkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Idola tak bisa melakukan\Napa pun untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percuma saja memuja mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dewa tidak turun untuk menemui manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi manusia tetap memberi mereka\Npersembahan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Prinsipnya sama saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maksudnya apa?\N- Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau mengobrol dengan pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua anak nakal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Padahal dahulu mereka sangat manis.\N- Utage, masakanmu lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sekarang mereka sangat tidak sopan.\N- Manfaatkan waktu untuk hal lebih berarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pochi, ayo kita jalan-jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membuang-buang tisu toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, kita berangkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan si kecil ini?\NIa manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak kalian sudah banyak mengurusku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia terlalu mencolok\N- Wajahnya kecil sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kalau berdiri di luar.\N- Dia tinggi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku membiarkannya masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini wajah asli atau efek komputer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau di rumahku?\NBagaimana kau tahu tempat ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengingat kepribadianmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat aneh kalau kau berhenti\Ntanpa memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang karena merasa khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bertanya ke agensimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mereka tak mau memberiku alamatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku membuntutimu dari sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, bukankah itu namanya menguntit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti pria hidung belang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kira kau bisa seenaknya\Nhanya karena kau tampan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sembarangan\Nhanya karena kau selebritas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan menunjuk orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka kembar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adik-adikku, Homare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku salah karena berhenti\Ntanpa sepatah kata pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan mengajak Pochi jalan-jalan.\NMinumlah teh selagi menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Homare, Yamato, bersihkan rumah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku menjelaskannya kepadanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku sangat senang\Nkarena idolaku mengkhawatirkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang karena khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini memang putus asa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak percaya\NKakak meninggalkan pekerjaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil dia melakukan itu\Nkecuali ada alasan mendesak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang tampan, tapi pasti\Nada yang salah dengan kepribadiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti buaya darat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga terlihat seperti\Norang yang suka memukul wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menakutkan. Mereka seram sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak mau membersihkan rumah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini, aku juga akan bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan saja padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ini bak mandi keluarga Utage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang dia bisa sangat menyeramkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar-benar pria mesum, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini foto lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aku, Yamato, dan Kakak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tua kami sibuk bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Kakak yang mengurus\Nserta memasak untuk kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sepertinya belakangan ini\Ndia mulai tidak peduli pada kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bersih-bersih dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali, Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?\NKau ingin kunyanyikan sebuah lagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau mau membunuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, buku itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh dari belakang lemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti buku resep tulisan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ini masih ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa menyenangkannya membaca buku resep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa seperti menemukan Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata Utage selalu seperti ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum bertemu Tamon…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memang agak berat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku sangat suka memasak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat orang memuji masakanku lezat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi ingin berusaha lebih keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau berhenti bekerja\Nsebagai pembantu karena diriku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuharap kau mau memikirkannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lakukan sesuatu demi orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkanlah apa yang sebenarnya\Ningin kau lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihatmu harus menahan diri karena aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku juga jadi tidak senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melihat senyummu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak selalu\Nterlalu memikirkan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesekali tidak apa-apa\Nbersikap egois, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru sadar\Nkalian sangat mengkhawatirkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak pekerjaan yang bisa dipilih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kenapa aku memilih
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjadi pembantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sangat terampil\Nmengurus pekerjaan rumah tangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih karena selalu\Nmenjaga rumahku tetap bersih, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin memindahkan\Nrak buku itu ke tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku saja yang pindahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anakku sangat suka kari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dan suamiku sibuk bekerja,\Njadi aku senang kau membantuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong buatkan kari ini lagi kapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus kembali berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf jika aku mengganggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang agak aneh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau sudah membereskan rumah kami,\Njadi kau orang yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena sempat mengira\Nkau suka memukul wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku tidak suka pria tampan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya apa? Kalian menyuruhnya bekerja?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon itu seperti dewa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta maaf kepadanya sekarang juga…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang karena bisa akur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan adik-adikmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya memukul wanita,\Ndia malah membuat kakaknya marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa, Homare, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar-benar orang yang aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya. Kakak, kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Demi kebaikan Tamon."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir ini adalah tindakan yang tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, kau tampak kurang sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tidak apa-apa…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berkeringat banyak sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hari libur,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tidak ada kegiatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, dengan Kinoshita di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Fujita.\NMaaf meneleponmu pagi-pagi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya satu permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semalam, Tamon kena flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku dan yang lain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak bisa menemaninya seharian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa tolong periksa kondisinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fujita yang meneleponku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memintaku menjengukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena kau harus repot-repot kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawakan obat dan minuman.\NSilakan diminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku permisi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau langsung pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita yang satunya lagi\Nmasih asyik minum kola di dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita, beristirahatlah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bersama Kinoshita yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ruangannya agak sesak karena ramai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi. Maaf mengganggu kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sedang bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita yang datang semalam\Nsedang tidur di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Kinoshita\Nyang datang pagi buta tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita yang baru datang duduk situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada orang lain di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di ruangan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya ada aku dan kau saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu, Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak Kinoshita di ruangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tamon.\N- Ada
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tuan Suram.\N- begitu banyak
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hottiehara.\N- Kinoshita
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yang mana sekarang?\N- di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- lebih aneh dari biasanya.\N- Banyak Kinoshita yang mengunjungiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas jatuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tak cuma anak yang merasakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan melakukan\Ntugas utamaku sekarang juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaanku membaik\Nsetelah selesai bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membuatkan berbagai jenis bubur.\NJika kau mau…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku pusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menatapku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahku tidak terlihat tampan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Hottiehara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku minta buburnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau boleh makan semangkuk,\Natau seratus mangkuk sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sungguh lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia sudah tenang. Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buburnya menetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau langsung dicuci, tidak akan berbekas…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, biar aku yang cuci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu, biar aku saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mencucinya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, kau harus istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demamnya juga sudah turun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demammu masih tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sepanas itu. Rasakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar suara lonceng Jetavana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tanganmu dingin. Terasa enak sekali.\N- Semuanya fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kulihat wajahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa lagi sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jadi berjerawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage yang lain tidak ada jerawatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kau yang tampak agak pucat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang lainnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus makan makanan bergizi\Ndan istirahat cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata dia masih berhalusinasi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya dia bisa tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang biasku,\Ntapi dia sangat merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta ternyata bisa sangat merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau tak melakukannya\Ndemi orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkanlah apa yang sebenarnya\Ningin kau lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini kupikir aku menjadi pembantu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi bisa memujamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sepertinya aku keliru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku hanya menjadikanmu alasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada kenyataannya,\Naku selalu melakukan hal yang kusuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan lewat dirimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa bertemu banyak orang menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau penggemar garis keras?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar penggemar idola yang payah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua berpacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan zombi temperamental ini\Nkepadamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi pembantu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata sangat menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sudah tak bisa kembali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maaf mengganggu.\N- Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini F/ACE dalam mode siap kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Nona Utage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka seenaknya buka pintu dan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena kau harus mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali tidak merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaiannya sudah rapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kalian sedang kerja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sedang jam istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lokasi syutingnya kebetulan dekat,\Njadi kami mau mampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah tertidur lelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage, kau sudah makan siang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kita makan bareng saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keito akan membuatkan makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, nanti penggemarmu bisa menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah. Jangan menolak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo duduk dan makan bersama kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gorila… Pengawal negara gorila.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tak enak sudah merepotkanmu\Ntapi tidak memberimu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, silakan dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo semuanya, makan selagi hangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah merepotkan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage, boleh pinjam piringmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kugambarkan beruang\Npakai saus tomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kubunuh kalian semua…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gagal, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku masih sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih tidak selera makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selera estetikaku\Njauh lebih baik daripada kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau malah mengabaikanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau aku menggambar di wajahmu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Rasakan ini…\N- Maaf, tolong ampuni aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan seenaknya naik ke meja\Natau memainkan makananmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua akan kubuang\Nseperti sampah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar cerewet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo cepat usir orang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat waktu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memang tampak bertengkar,\Ntapi sebenarnya saling memedulikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tetap saja aku berharap\Nmereka bisa sedikit lebih tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon sedang butuh tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Pak Tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau foto-foto untuk blogku.\NBoleh pinjam wajahmu sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang kau panggil pria tua?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangunlah, Pak Tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh pinjam wajahmu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu sekali… Ayo diunggah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa hilang kepercayaan\Npada umat manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan diminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara soal itu,\Nbukankah seharusnya kita menanyakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fujita memberi tahu kami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau kau berhenti jadi pembantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal masalah itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}secara pribadi aku sangat ingin\Nkau kembali bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejadian Tamon pingsan kali ini
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti ada kaitannya dengan itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Utage mungkin ada urusan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski rasanya sedikit sepi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak perlu memaksakan diri\Ndemi seorang Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku tahu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melakukan pekerjaanmu dengan bangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tiba-tiba mengundurkan diri,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti ada sebuah alasan\Nyang tak bisa dihindari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja aku tak berniat\Nmenanyakan alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Norang ini tak pantas mendapatkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sana, pergilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kenapa semua orang kumpul di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kau sudah sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah merasa mendingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan kelemahanku ini!\NAku sungguh minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf juga karena aku cuti tanpa izin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku siap menebusnya dengan nyawaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang, kami kemari bukan\Nuntuk menceramahimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu apa tujuan kalian kemari?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba lihat ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daun bawang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya kukira itu sekadar rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ternyata sangat efektif, ya.\N- Ada daun bawang di lehernya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga sangat enak\Nkalau dibuat jadi sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti menertawakanku dan diamlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dariku, agar kau lekas sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah yang banyak agar cepat sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sok peduli\Npakai hadiah main pachinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perbaiki dulu kelemahanmu pakai ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Disimpan untuk nanti saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini titipan dari Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong serahkan kepadanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-teman, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua begitu baik kepadaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini aku merasa dianggap manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah merasa baikan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapku tak akan berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa bahagia yang selama ini kudapatkan\Ndari dirimu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan selamanya kusimpan di dalam hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa pun yang menjadi keputusanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan tetap baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menangis tersedu-sedu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mataku perih gara-gara daun bawangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan padaku. Aku akan buat sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, hidungmu meler, tuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyimpannya erat-erat di hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan mengundurkan diri
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari pekerjaanku sebagai pembantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua berkat bantuanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akhirnya menyadari hal yang penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pertama-tama, aku harus bertanya\Napa aku bisa kembali bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, ada telepon dari agensi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, dengan Kinoshita di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena meneleponmu tiba-tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu ini sangat merepotkan,\Ntapi aku punya permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Toda ternyata mengalami patah tulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya. Baik, aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku boleh melanjutkan tugasku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Percuma saja aku mengkhawatirkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tahu cepat atau lambat\Nkau akan melakukan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhati-hatilah mulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai kau melakukan kesalahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berlebihan.\NJangan terlalu memaksakan dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah membulatkan tekadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai saat ini,\Naku masih menantikan bimbinganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang tak bisa\Nmenyingkirkan perasaanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku masih bisa menyembunyikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau menangis,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak akan menyeka air matamu itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku akan meminjamkan saputangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}izinkanlah aku tetap berada di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin dalam cinta yang dirasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin menyakitkan pula rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kadang kala, aku sangat ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berlari menjauh dari sisimu karena itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong bimbing aku lagi untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mulai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan terus ada bersamamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyemangatimu.
